1. *Čini* mi se da će sutra biti sunčano. (It seems to me that it will be sunny tomorrow.)
2. Kako *činiš* da je ovo teško pitanje? (How do you make this question difficult?)
3. Ona *čini* sve što može da pomogne drugima. (She does everything she can to help others.)
4. *Čini* mi se da nisam dovoljno spavao sinoć. (It seems to me that I didn't sleep enough last night.)
5. Njihova dobra volja *čini* ovaj projekat uspešnim. (Their good will makes this project successful.)
6. Način na koji on *čini* svoj posao je neverovatan. (The way he does his job is amazing.)
7. Kada sam bio mali, mislio sam da se Božić *čini* samo u snovima. (When I was little, I thought that Christmas only happened in dreams.)
8. Njegova sposobnost da *čini* ljudima ugodno uvek me fascinira. (His ability to make people feel comfortable always fascinates me.)
9. Ono što *čini* ovaj film posebnim je njegova muzika. (What makes this movie special is its music.)
10. Šta bi *činilo* da se osećate srećnim? (What would make you feel happy?)